OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776712271
OL,3,CWoman arrested after death of 14-week-
OL,4,Cold baby girl
OL,6,FIn a statement, the force said: "A 36
OL,7,Fyear-old woman has been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of child neglect and remains
OL,9,Fin custody.
OL,11,F"A scene will remain in place whilst
OL,12,Fwe conduct our investigation, which is
OL,13,Fstill in its early stages.
OL,15,F"We are keeping an open mind and
OL,16,Ffollowing all available lines of
OL,17,Fenquiry at this time."
